Using Unity
<dl>
    <dt>Press the Super (Windows) Key or click on the Ubuntu logo on the Unity panel and search Software Sources</dt>
    <dt>Ensure that the universe and multiverse sources are enabled</dt>
    <dt>Click on Ubuntu Software Center on the Unity panel</dt>
    <dt>Search for and install cheese</dt>
    <dt>Close Ubuntu Software center</dt>
    <dt>Press the Super (Windows) Key or click on the Ubuntu logo on the Unity panel and search Cheese</dt>
        <dd>Verify the camera image should be displayed properly</dd>
    <dt>Close "cheese"</dt>
        <dd>Verify that the webcam image is displayed correctly. </dd>
</dl>

